OL,3,CWhich countries are paying athletes
OL,4,Cfor winning gold at the Olympics?
OL,6,FThere have been calls in recent years
OL,7,Ffor Olympic medallists across all
OL,8,Fsports to receive prize money, with
OL,9,Ftennis great Martina Navratilova
OL,10,Fsaying that being a top athlete now is
OL,11,Fa "full-time job".
OL,13,F"The days of amateurs have gone," she
OL,14,Fcontinued.
OL,16,F"The Olympics have always been the
OL,17,Fbiggest sports event and the athletes
OL,18,Fwere the only ones not making money."
