OL,3,CWhich countries are paying athletes
OL,4,Cfor winning gold at the Olympics?
OL,6,FWorld Athletics announced earlier this
OL,7,Fyear that it would be the first sport
OL,8,Fto offer Olympic prize money in Games
OL,9,Fhistory at Paris, with winners in the
OL,10,F48 disciplines to receive $50,000
OL,11,F(#39,400).
OL,13,FHow much are countries paying their
OL,14,Fwinning athletes?
OL,16,FAccording to Forbes, who reached out
OL,17,Fto all 206 countries and territories
OL,18,Fparticipating in this year's games, 33
OL,19,Fconfirmed they will pay their athletes
OL,20,Ffor winning gold.
