OL,6,FWhat other prizes are given to winning
OL,7,Fathletes?
OL,9,FMeanwhile, some countries opt to
OL,10,Freward their athletes with other types
OL,11,Fof benefits, such as holiday vouchers
OL,12,Fand pensions.
OL,14,FPoland offers gold medallists roughly
OL,15,F$82,000 (#63,900), but beyond that,
OL,16,Feach medallist in Paris will be given
OL,17,Fa holiday voucher for two from a
OL,18,Ftravel agency.
